snippet.title: Super Mario and the Elemental Orbs - NCFC 2015 Trailer
snippet.description:
The demo has been released! Download it here: http://www.nintendocfc.com/booth.html?id=90

A trailer for SMEO at 2015's NCFC. During this event (starting August 24th), you can download the game on http://www.nintendocfc.com/ . You will also be able to see all new features and changes on this website.
